which, I should note, have already demoted the site featured in that thread=
).

AI-generated content, though, will likely push the situation past the break=
ing point: yes, the amount of money that can be made from advertising by an=
y individual page is continually decreasing, but if pages can be produced f=
or no marginal cost than the number of pages that will be produced is effec=
tively infinite.

